{"tid":1630630,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"私了唔好比人影到","createTime":"2019-10-06T13:05:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T13:23:42.000Z","uid":249883,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"bf23ad2a1522af40ccf55e148903ea5cb6244400","tid":1630630,"uid":249883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:05:57.000Z","msg":"私了唔好比人影到，你地打到爆曬頭，比鏡頭影出嚟唔好睇，打到頭都爆埋，人地就覺得你暴力，要c鳥，打睇唔到嘅位，內傷，唔好打頭，斷關節，骨節。"},{"pid":"94018b34f9bd66df5185d9946f81b7a23ab838e6","tid":1630630,"uid":249883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:06:07.000Z","msg":"推10"},{"pid":"c9336a2d1d1d3b2513355043360e3535e7ab2180","tid":1630630,"uid":249883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:06:19.000Z","msg":"推9"},{"pid":"8329488997cb2c3866d93bb4e24b12ca4ab119cd","tid":1630630,"uid":249883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:06:39.000Z","msg":"推8"},{"pid":"bfe2bcb3161838d2d25174c6ba098bf3e110cb63","tid":1630630,"uid":249883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:06:58.000Z","msg":"推7"},{"pid":"884d5f0c6ab818dfc781f3e83da47c7d5ffef1ba","tid":1630630,"uid":249883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:07:11.000Z","msg":"推6"},{"pid":"2d455ca71c88bedd747f82e11b07cd2bcd05a0aa","tid":1630630,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:07:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家 呢幾日都係行動日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但連登都無比大陸DDos攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就證明左係大量五毛做緊野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又分化又風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">我地係時候要醒下<br />\n<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">跟住就係開始做正經野：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 推紅色的士撞人單野<br />\n<br />\n2.推黑警又當街踢人單野<br />\n<br />\n3.九龍塘軍營入面有綠色防暴警既片<br />\n<br />\n4.解釋返裝修既原因比外國知<br />\n<br />\n5.宣傳黑紅藍黃既概念</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />光復香港，時代革命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地唔好再比五毛搞爆連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"6e56a02a4387441e90b09aab4da415c4b4b62662","tid":1630630,"uid":249883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:07:23.000Z","msg":"推5"},{"pid":"d56737473f19068ea8137cfa513af116ac4c3fc3","tid":1630630,"uid":293667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:07:36.000Z","msg":"係自衛<br />\n講左好多次口罩遮唔到幾多<br />\n要做事的話 最低消費帽+面巾<br />\n<br />\n［停一停諗一諗］花少少時間睇 你覺得政府係咪真係冇做野？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630572\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630572</a><br />\n<br />\n［花10秒睇保護自已］千祈唔好以為啲狗好蠢 其實佢哋不斷做緊嘢<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1617712\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1617712</a><br />\n<br />\n[重開][全民上鎖]立即將你嘅SIM card上鎖！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1618689\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1618689</a>"},{"pid":"fc6405acda357fdcf7f03e606058b83e67c616f6","tid":1630630,"uid":249883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:07:43.000Z","msg":"推4"},{"pid":"f4e31925d15fb36784f68e1afc39e988896c23ae","tid":1630630,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:08:23.000Z","msg":"【行動】盡快整理所